Information: ABT-263 (Navitoclax) is a potent inhibitor of Bcl-xL; Bcl-2 and Bcl-w with Ki of _ 0.5 nM; _1 nM and _1 nM; but binds more weakly to Mcl-1 and A1. Phase 1/2.
SGX-523 is a selective Met inhibitor with IC50 of 4 nM; no activity to BRAFV599E; c-Raf; Abl and p38_. Phase 1.
OSI-930 is a potent inhibitor of Kit; KDR and CSF-1R with IC50 of 80 nM; 9 nM and 15 nM; respectively; also potent to Flt-1; c-Raf and Lck and low activity against PDGFR_/_; Flt-3 and Abl. Phase 1.
Epothilone B is a Taxol-like microtubule-stabilizing agent with EC0.01 of 1.8 _M. Phase 2.
Dyphylline is a xanthine derivative with bronchodilator and vasodilator effects.
Zolmitriptan(Zomig) is a selective serotonin receptor agonist.
Simvastatin is a competitive inhibitor of HMG-CoA reductase with Ki of 0.1-0.2 nM .
Nicorandil is potassium channel activator.
Cisatracurium Besylate is a nondepolarizing neuromuscular blocking agent; antagonizing the action of acetylcholine by inhibiting neuromuscular transmission.
Arbutin is a tyrosinase inhibitor with an IC50 of 1.09 mM.
Butylscopolamine bromide; is a peripherally acting antimuscarinic; anticholinergic agent used as an abdominal-specific antispasmodic.
Roxithromycin  is a semi-synthetic macrolide antibiotic. It is used to treat respiratory tract; urinary and soft tissue infections.
PNU-120596 is a positive allosteric modulator of _7 nAChR with EC50 of 216 nM.

SB705498 is a TRPV1 antagonist for hTRPV1; antagonizes capsaicin; acid; and heat activation of TRPV1 with IC50 of 3 nM; 0.1 nM and 6 nM; shows a degree of voltage dependence; exhibits >100-fold selectivity for TRPV1 over TRPM8. Phase 2.
CCG 50014 is a potent and selective inhibitor of RGS4 with IC50 of 30 nM.
Oxybutynin is an anticholinergic medication used to relieve urinary and bladder difficulties.
Pheniramine Maleate is an antihistamine with anticholinergic properties used to treat allergic conditions such as hay fever or urticaria.
Doxofylline is a phosphodiesterase inhibitor and a xanthine derivative drug for asthma.
Brimonidine Tartrate is a highly selective ?-adrenergic receptor agonist with EC50 of 0.45 nM for the ?2A adrenoreceptor; and used to treat open-angle glaucoma or ocular hypertension.

Information: IWP-2 is an inhibitor of Wnt processing and secretion with IC50 of 27 nM; selective blockage of Porcn-mediated Wnt palmitoylation; does not affect Wnt/_-catenin in general and displays no effect against Wnt-stimulated cellular responses.
SGC-CBP30 is a potent CREBBP/EP300 inhibitor with IC50 of 21 nM and 38 nM; respectively.
FH1(BRD-K4477) is a small molecule; which promotes differentiation of iPS-derived hepatocytes.
Lomeguatrib is a potent inhibitor of O6-alkylguanine-DNA-alkyltransferase with IC50 of 5 nM.
ABT-737 is a BH3 mimetic inhibitor of Bcl-xL; Bcl-2 and Bcl-w with EC50 of 78.7 nM; 30.3 nM and 197.8 nM; respectively; no inhibition observed against Mcl-1; Bcl-B or Bfl-1. Phase 2.
GSK690693 is a pan-Akt inhibitor targeting Akt1/2/3 with IC50 of 2 nM/13 nM/9 nM; also sensitive to the AGC kinase family: PKA; PrkX and PKC isozymes. Phase 1.
Dacarbazine is an antineoplastic chemotherapy drug used in the treatment of various cancers.
BMS-707035 is a specific HIV-I integrase (IN) inhibitor with IC50 of 15 nM. Phase 2.
Aztreonam is a synthetic monocyclic beta-lactam antibiotic.
Telbivudine is an antiviral agent used in the treatment of hepatitis B infection.
Ramipril is an angiotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) inhibitor with IC50 of 5 nM.
Tamoxifen Citrate is an antagonist of the estrogen receptor by competitive inhibition of estrogen binding.
Dronedarone HCl is a therapy for the treatment of patients with paroxysmal and persistent atrial fibrillation or atrial flutter.
Artemether is an antimalarial for the treatment of resistant strains of falciparum malaria.
Dioscin is a saponin extracted and isolated from Polygonatum Zanlanscianense Pamp; showing antitumor activities.
Scopolamine hydrobromide is a competitive muscarinic acetylcholine receptor with an IC50 of 55.3 ± 4.3 nM.
GW3965 is a potent; selective LXRagonist for hLXR_ and hLXR_ with EC50 of 190 and 30 nM; respectively.

MK-2461 is a potent; multi-targeted inhibitor for c-Met(WT/mutants) with IC50 of 0.4-2.5 nM; less potent to Ron; Flt1; 8- to 30-fold greater selectivity of c-Met targets versus FGFR1; FGFR2; FGFR3; PDGFR_; KDR; Flt3; Flt4; TrkA; and TrkB. Phase 1/2.

Ranolazine(Ranexa) is an antianginal medication.
Meglumine is an amino sugar derived from sorbitol for THP-1 cells with IC50 of 22 _g/mL.

Asiatic acid is the aglycone of asiaticoside isolated from the plant Centella asiatica; commonly used in wound healing.
D-Mannitol is an osmotic diuretic agent and a weak renal vasodilator.
Spectinomycin HCl is a new parenteral antibiotic prepared from Streptomyces spectabilis.

Carbimazole is an imidazole antithyroid agent.
Cyromazine is a triazine insect growth regulator used as an insecticide and an acaricide.
Vinorelbine Tartrate is a semi-synthetic vinca alkaloid; and inhibits mitosis through interaction with tubulin.
UNC1215 is a potent and selective MBT (malignant brain tumor) antagonist; which binds L3MBTL3 with IC50 of 40 nM and Kd of 120 nM; 50-fold selective versus other members of the human MBT family.
Beta-Lapachone is a selective DNA topoisomerase I inhibitor; exhibiting no inhibitory activities against DNA topoisomerase II or ligase. Phase 2.
VER-49009 is a potent HSP90 inhibitor with IC50 of 47 nM for HSP90_.
Nutlin-3a; the active enantiomer of Nutlin-3; inhibits the p53/MDM2 interaction with IC50 of 90 nM.

Cyclosporine (Neoral) is an immunosuppressant drug.
Phenylbutazone(Butazolidin; Butatron) is used as a non-steroidal anti-inflammatory agent for the treatment of chronic pain; including the symptoms of arthritis.
Ranitidine is a histamine H2-receptor antagonist with IC50 of 3.3 ± 1.4 _M.
Aripiprazole is a human 5-HT1A receptor partial agonist with a Ki of 4.2 nM.
Probucol is an anti-hyperlipidemic drug by lowering the level of cholesterol in the bloodstream by increasing the rate of LDL catabolism.
Azomycin is an antimicrobial antibiotic produced by a strain of Nocardia mesenterica.

Tenoxicam is a good HO. radicals scavenger with an IC50 of 56.7 _M
NPS 2143 is a novel potent and selective antagonist of Ca(2+) receptor with IC50 of 43 nM.

Valdecoxib is a potent and selective inhibitor of COX-2 with IC50 of 5 nM.
Teriflunomide is the active metabolite of leflunomide; inhibiting pyrimidine de novo synthesis by blocking the enzyme dihydroorotate dehydrogenase; used as an immunomodulatory agent.
